{"tid":1275954,"cid":10,"subCid":0,"title":"[隻狼劇情]同丈締結不死既係隻猿定巴?","createTime":"2019-07-02T00:29:57.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-03T14:14:32.000Z","uid":158008,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"a6ddd833210bcb7d621c138fdcafdac33c220a48","tid":1275954,"uid":158008,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-02T00:29:57.000Z","msg":"上一代有不死之力既丈想斬斷不死, 係劇情推進理解巴搵左好多方法去幫佢斬斷不死, 雖然搵到要既材料, 但獨欠不死斬<br />\n<br />\n問題來啦, 當年攞唔到不死斬又點斬斷不死?<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n第二, 鵰佛師應該係有份去搵方法去幫佢主人丈斬斷不死, 打屏風猴子時個僧人有講之前有忍者都想來挑戰但失敗, 應該係想講鵰佛師吧<br />\n<br />\n而鵰佛師之所以放棄做忍者, 就好似其中一個結局咁因為佢要殺左丈先可以幫佢斬斷不死, 最後因為失去主人而鵰佛<br />\n<br />\n咁其實當年同丈締結不死係巴定隻猿? 而無不死斬又點斬斷不死? 同埋最後落手係巴定隻猿?"},{"pid":"ae9b07c1b4f83f8a2fb53ec8b570ba3504b22530","tid":1275954,"uid":141723,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-02T00:40:28.000Z","msg":"鵰佛師 唔係因為修羅先鵰佛咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"139b78f82e65141a38ef12018a2423fa0eeb2f86","tid":1275954,"uid":75050,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-02T00:54:32.000Z","msg":"鵰師佛<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"70fc3ea748b849d68ea2cceb7206fc5e82efd9e8","tid":1275954,"uid":75050,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-02T00:57:48.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://www.yxdown.com/gonglue/449996_3.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.yxdown.com%2Fgonglue%2F449996_3.html&d=9Ou39NWu4C7Ce3sh0Mn9C1e0bVP%2BLlUkdLfYKyPPBhg%3D&h=fb1993da\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.yxdown.com/gonglue/449996_3.html</a>"},{"pid":"c5318e3dcecb3f1fb062bc9bc5124528be676565","tid":1275954,"uid":75050,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"70fc3ea748b849d68ea2cceb7206fc5e82efd9e8","tid":1275954,"uid":75050,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-02T00:57:48.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://www.yxdown.com/gonglue/449996_3.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.yxdown.com%2Fgonglue%2F449996_3.html&d=9Ou39NWu4C7Ce3sh0Mn9C1e0bVP%2BLlUkdLfYKyPPBhg%3D&h=fb1993da\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.yxdown.com/gonglue/449996_3.html</a>"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-02T00:58:59.000Z","msg":"巴用開門自殺，同隻狼自殺結局一樣，丈變返正常人"},{"pid":"178535d60418c754376114e06fe16c76c5054e34","tid":1275954,"uid":158008,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c5318e3dcecb3f1fb062bc9bc5124528be676565","tid":1275954,"uid":75050,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"70fc3ea748b849d68ea2cceb7206fc5e82efd9e8","tid":1275954,"uid":75050,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-02T00:57:48.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://www.yxdown.com/gonglue/449996_3.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.yxdown.com%2Fgonglue%2F449996_3.html&d=9Ou39NWu4C7Ce3sh0Mn9C1e0bVP%2BLlUkdLfYKyPPBhg%3D&h=fb1993da\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.yxdown.com/gonglue/449996_3.html</a>"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-02T00:58:59.000Z","msg":"巴用開門自殺，同隻狼自殺結局一樣，丈變返正常人"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-02T02:27:37.000Z","msg":"明白<br />\n上網睇有人覺得佛雕師係丈既忍者, 同佢締結不死, 巴係丈既戀人, 巴同佛雕師都一同找斬斷不死既方法, 最後就好似隻狼其中一個結局咁佛雕師斬斷不死親手殺死丈, 所以決定放棄再做忍者, 咁就好似呼應到隻猿隻狼兩者結局<br />\n<br />\n但其實呢個講法應該唔太合理, 因為如果係咁, 巴就唔會死<br />\n<br />\n照推測應該巴先係締結不死之人<br />\n<br />\n佛雕師應該純粹係丈身邊既一個忍者, 因為殺得太多人差點落入修羅"},{"pid":"d19c64e671186a79fb54f2b03c8fcc55cec094a9","tid":1275954,"uid":91753,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"139b78f82e65141a38ef12018a2423fa0eeb2f86","tid":1275954,"uid":75050,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-02T00:54:32.000Z","msg":"鵰師佛<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-02T02:51:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/35.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/36.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />啵一聲笑咗出來"},{"pid":"f06b582b99c576230354e6e9005d44659c7b7533","tid":1275954,"uid":3768,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-03T14:14:32.000Z","msg":"條龍其實係咪中國飄過去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}